data.description: Rare Find! Spacious Moduline home with 3 beds. 2 baths and just shy of 1800 sq.ft. of living. Open concept living, lovely bamboo flooring, large kitchen with island, vaulted ceilings, spacious family room, separate living room and pellet stove to keep you warm on cold winter days. Step out to the private and secluded 2.29 acres on Indian Creek and Woodland Trail. Plenty of space for a shop. Great end of the road location, close to highly desired Olympia schools, minutes to downtown shopping. This is a must see!
